d0e788a1c980":{"observation":{"concepts":["health check","microservice metrics","circuit breaker","latency monitoring"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Executed 'rtk curl -fsSL http://localhost:3111/agentmemory/health' to check status.","Service is running and connected, with 'circuitBreaker' in a 'closed' state.","The 'mem::compress' function has a high failure rate: 77 failures out of 156 total calls (avg latency ~64.6s).","KV connectivity is healthy with a latency of 2.01 ms.","Full curl command output log is saved at '/Users/zasuo/Library/Application Support/rtk/tee/1779357970_curl.log'."],"files":["/Users/zasuo/Library/Application Support/rtk/tee/1779357970_curl.log"],"id":"obs_mpfbslbe_d0e788a1c980","importance":4,"narrative":"A curl command was executed to inspect the health of the local agentmemory service. While the service is connected and KV database latency is low, the memory compression function (mem::compress) displays a high failure rate and high latency, which could indicate performance or connectivity issues during compression tasks.","sessionId":"019e49d8-e7a0-71d1-a19e-64b2b9af690e","subtitle":"Executed curl request against local agentmemory service","timestamp":"2026-05-21T10:06:10.886Z","title":"Check agentmemory health status via HTTP endpoint","type":"command_run"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mpfbslbk_8eb545aa0375":{"observation":{"concepts":["AgentMemory troubleshooting","ECONNREFUSED","process management","OpenTelemetry"],"confidence":1,"facts":["AgentMemory proxy encountered ECONNREFUSED connection failures on port 3111 for multiple endpoints.","OpenTelemetry disconnected from the engine due to WebSocket errors and attempted reconnection.","Stale AgentMemory workers with PIDs 19618 and 19652 were stopped and killed during setup.","The iii-engine process was started successfully and registered a new worker ID."],"files":["/Users/zasuo/.agentmemory/server.log"],"id":"obs_mpfbslbk_8eb545aa0375","importance":5,"narrative":"The rtk tail command read the 